I need to identify input fields for space and charges, a calculate button, and a save button. Then I will produce a JSON array containing click actions for each of the identified selectors.
<OUTPUT_JSON>[{"action": "click", "selector": "input[name*=space i], input[placeholder*=space i]", "text": ""}, {"action": "click", "selector": "input[name*=charge i]", "text": ""}, {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"calculate\" i), button:has-text(\"compute\" i)"}, {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"save\" i)"}]</OUTPUT_JSON>
